name: Duct Tape
description: Duct Tape is a joint collaboration between Jason Boehning  and John Pierson. Most of the ideas for nodes are Jason's as he is the MEP guru, and the coding is done by both Jason and John. The idea behind Duct Tape started in August 2017 at BiLTNA, and represents a unique collaboration between two friends from different backgrounds who are over 800 miles apart.
